26
00:01:23,080 --> 00:01:27,419
Havia bufões, havia improvisadores,
havia bailarinos, havia músicos,

27
00:01:27,420 --> 00:01:29,459
havia Beleza, havia vinho.

28
00:01:29,460 --> 00:01:32,439
